README - MySQL
-----------------------------

- The socket is in the following locations:
	- OS X: /Applications/CCW/data/plugins/MySQL/tmp/mysql.sock
	- Windows: [CCW Base Directory]\data\plugins\MySQL\tmp\mysql.sock
	
- Default port is 3306

- Username : root
- Password : root

- Options may be edited in plugins/MySQL/my.ini

- Remember changes made to my.ini may affect the PHP configuration